---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Popcorn Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw
description: Taco night has been transformed! Crispy bites of chicken have been coated in a sticky Sichuan paste for bags of flavour, before
being nestled inside warm tortillas with a creamy and tangy slaw. It’s another taco-tastic dinner!

